# Adventuring Gear

The difference between a successful expedition and a disaster often comes down to preparation. Rope to cross the chasm, torches to light the darkness, healing supplies to treat wounds—the mundane equipment you carry matters as much as your weapons and armor.

Gear kits bundle essential equipment into convenient packages. Rather than itemizing every piece of rope, piton, and ration, kits provide complete loadouts for specific roles and situations at economical prices.

